OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FA 32-year-old woman has been given the
OL,7,Fall-clear from cancer after undergoing
OL,8,Fthe UK's first liver transplant for
OL,9,Fadvanced bowel cancer.
OL,11,FBianca Perea, a trainee lawyer from
OL,12,FManchester, was diagnosed with stage
OL,13,Ffour bowel cancer in November 2021.
OL,15,FThe cancer had spread to all eight
OL,16,Fsegments of her liver, leaving her
OL,17,Fwith limited treatment options.
