OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FBut, after receiving targeted drug
OL,7,Ftherapy, chemotherapy, and surgery,
OL,8,Fshe underwent a successful liver
OL,9,Ftransplant last summer at Leeds
OL,10,FTeaching Hospitals NHS Trust and now
OL,11,Fshows no signs of cancer.
OL,13,FMs Perea first visited her GP in Wigan
OL,14,Fwith symptoms including bloating and
OL,15,Fchanges in bowel habits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
