OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FShe initially sought medical advice
OL,7,Fafter feeling constipated and bloated.
OL,8,FFollowing a colonoscopy and biopsy,
OL,9,Fdoctors diagnosed her with advanced
OL,10,Fbowel cancer that had spread to her
OL,11,Fliver.
OL,13,F"I remember everything slowing down
OL,14,Fwhen I was told," she said. "The
OL,15,Fdoctor said they were looking to
OL,16,Fprolong my life rather than cure the
OL,17,Fcancer. But I refused to believe that
OL,18,Fwas the end of the road."
