OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FShe was then referred to the Christie
OL,7,FNHS Foundation Trust's local treatment
OL,8,Fcentre in Wigan in early December 2021.
OL,10,FMs Perea underwent 37 rounds of a
OL,11,Ftargeted drug called panitumumab
OL,12,Falongside chemotherapy for two and a
OL,13,Fhalf years, resulting in a significant
OL,14,Freduction in the cancer.
OL,16,FIn May 2023, she had surgery to remove
OL,17,Fthe primary bowel tumour, but
OL,18,Finoperable tumours remained in her
OL,19,Fliver.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
