OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FDue to her remarkable response to
OL,7,Ftreatment, doctors considered a liver
OL,8,Ftransplant - a procedure not typically
OL,9,Fperformed for bowel cancer patients.
OL,11,FShe was added to the transplant list
OL,12,Fin February 2024 and underwent surgery
OL,13,Flater that summer.
OL,15,F"Within four weeks, I was able to
OL,16,Fdrive and walk the family dogs," Ms
OL,17,FPerea said. "To go from being told I
OL,18,Fhad limited time to live to now being
OL,19,Fcancer-free is the greatest gift."
