OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,FThe success of Ms Perea's treatment
OL,7,Frepresents a significant advancement
OL,8,Fin the fight against advanced bowel
OL,9,Fcancer.
OL,11,FDr Kalena Marti, her oncologist at the
OL,12,FChristie NHS Foundation Trust, said
OL,13,Fthe case highlights the potential of
OL,14,Fliver transplants in specific cancer
OL,15,Fcases.
OL,17,F"When we examined the tumour cells in
OL,18,Fher liver, they weren't active," Dr
OL,19,FMarti said.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@`O]
