OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,F"This is excellent news, and we hope
OL,7,Fthis means the cancer won't return.
OL,8,FWhile advanced bowel cancer is
OL,9,Fcomplex, this breakthrough shows how
OL,10,Fpersonalized treatments can make a
OL,11,Fdifference."
OL,13,FDr Ian Rowe, a consultant hepatologist
OL,14,Fat Leeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust,
OL,15,Fpraised the importance of organ
OL,16,Fdonation in making such treatments
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]
