OL,3,CWoman beats cancer with groundbreaking
OL,4,Cliver transplant
OL,6,F"Organ donation saves lives," he said.
OL,7,F"Bianca's case underscores why it's
OL,8,Fessential for people to register their
OL,9,Fdecision to donate and discuss it with
OL,10,Ftheir families."
OL,12,FNow cancer-free, Ms Perea is focused
OL,13,Fon rebuilding her life. She is
OL,14,Fimproving her fitness and planning her
OL,15,Ffirst holiday in years.
OL,17,F"My liver is doing really well," she
OL,18,Fsaid. "I've had my second scan, and
OL,19,Fit's all clear. I've been given a
OL,20,Fsecond chance, and I'm going to grab
OL,21,Fit with both hands."
